    <item>
      <title>习近平承诺将把青年就业作为首要政策重点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/china-s-xi-pledges-to-make-youth-employment-a-top-priority</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平在 7 月份的一次重要政策会议上承诺优先考虑青年就业问题，并投入更多资源创造就业机会，这增强了人们对该领域改革的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/china-s-xi-pledges-to-make-youth-employment-a-top-priority</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 11:00:09 GMT</pubDate>
